{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/2012-12-23-dashlane-easter-egg-konami-code-reveals-conways-game-of-life/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"tjrobinson.net","author":"Tom Robinson"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"73b1688a-ad4a-56c0-9846-8d65f27d07c1","excerpt":"I’ve been a Dashlane user for a while now, having found out about it through a friend and respected colleague who started working for them in the Paris office…","html":"<p>I’ve been a <a href=\"https://www.dashlane.com/\">Dashlane</a> user for a while now, having found out about it through a friend and respected colleague who started working for them in the Paris office.</p>\n<p>What you may not know is that Dashlane have invited a number of people to be on their “Board of Users” and to give feedback on new product developments. A few days ago one of the QA Engineers set us all a challenge - to find a hidden “cheat code” in the PC version of the application.</p>\n<p>Well, I found it! (and I think I was the first)</p>\n<p>It turns out that if you open the application, then go to the <em>Help</em> > <em>About</em> screen you’ll initially see this:</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 316px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c6dc37479af4a36618c6a4eadebb93a7/67145/about-before.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 91.21621621621621%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"A Dashlane screenshot\"\n        title=\"A Dashlane screenshot\"\n        src=\"/static/c6dc37479af4a36618c6a4eadebb93a7/67145/about-before.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c6dc37479af4a36618c6a4eadebb93a7/12f09/about-before.png 148w,\n/static/c6dc37479af4a36618c6a4eadebb93a7/e4a3f/about-before.png 295w,\n/static/c6dc37479af4a36618c6a4eadebb93a7/67145/about-before.png 316w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 316px) 100vw, 316px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Now comes the fun part, you need to type the <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Konami_Code\">Konami Code</a>:</p>\n<p>↑ ↑ ↓ ↓ ← → ← → B A</p>\n<p>As soon as you finish that, you’ll see this screen and the <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Easter_egg_(media)\">Easter Egg</a> will have been activated:</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 316px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f5781cdd39be913b7f92b55d2075af06/67145/about-after.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 91.21621621621621%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"A Dashlane screenshot\"\n        title=\"A Dashlane screenshot\"\n        src=\"/static/f5781cdd39be913b7f92b55d2075af06/67145/about-after.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f5781cdd39be913b7f92b55d2075af06/12f09/about-after.png 148w,\n/static/f5781cdd39be913b7f92b55d2075af06/e4a3f/about-after.png 295w,\n/static/f5781cdd39be913b7f92b55d2075af06/67145/about-after.png 316w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 316px) 100vw, 316px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Initially I though, hmm, interesting, is it some kind of icon editor? You can start drawing on the grid, like this:</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 316px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f7fa903ac59599f081574312b8a8b788/67145/about-start.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 91.21621621621621%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"A Dashlane screenshot\"\n        title=\"A Dashlane screenshot\"\n        src=\"/static/f7fa903ac59599f081574312b8a8b788/67145/about-start.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f7fa903ac59599f081574312b8a8b788/12f09/about-start.png 148w,\n/static/f7fa903ac59599f081574312b8a8b788/e4a3f/about-start.png 295w,\n/static/f7fa903ac59599f081574312b8a8b788/67145/about-start.png 316w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 316px) 100vw, 316px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>But as soon as you click the Dashlane logo then the grid turns into Conway’s Game of Life:</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 316px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/33f5da561e44a56e80898ae45506656e/67145/about-running.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 91.21621621621621%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"A Dashlane screenshot\"\n        title=\"A Dashlane screenshot\"\n        src=\"/static/33f5da561e44a56e80898ae45506656e/67145/about-running.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/33f5da561e44a56e80898ae45506656e/12f09/about-running.png 148w,\n/static/33f5da561e44a56e80898ae45506656e/e4a3f/about-running.png 295w,\n/static/33f5da561e44a56e80898ae45506656e/67145/about-running.png 316w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 316px) 100vw, 316px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>The guys at Dashlane have been kind enough to offer to send me some goodies but the main prize is this signed Dashlane drawing from the team at Dashlane in Paris:</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b3d3e6a403309e09319e3fb2d48a2fe2/aa15b/Dashlane-Konami-Code-Scan.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 121.62162162162163%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Dashlane Konami Code Scan\"\n        title=\"Dashlane Konami Code Scan\"\n        src=\"/static/b3d3e6a403309e09319e3fb2d48a2fe2/1c72d/Dashlane-Konami-Code-Scan.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b3d3e6a403309e09319e3fb2d48a2fe2/a80bd/Dashlane-Konami-Code-Scan.jpg 148w,\n/static/b3d3e6a403309e09319e3fb2d48a2fe2/1c91a/Dashlane-Konami-Code-Scan.jpg 295w,\n/static/b3d3e6a403309e09319e3fb2d48a2fe2/1c72d/Dashlane-Konami-Code-Scan.jpg 590w,\n/static/b3d3e6a403309e09319e3fb2d48a2fe2/a8a14/Dashlane-Konami-Code-Scan.jpg 885w,\n/static/b3d3e6a403309e09319e3fb2d48a2fe2/fbd2c/Dashlane-Konami-Code-Scan.jpg 1180w,\n/static/b3d3e6a403309e09319e3fb2d48a2fe2/aa15b/Dashlane-Konami-Code-Scan.jpg 2052w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Thanks all!</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Dashlane Easter Egg - Conway's Game of Life","date":"December 2012"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2012-12-23-dashlane-easter-egg-konami-code-reveals-conways-game-of-life/","previous":{"fileAbsolutePath":"/home/runner/work/tjrobinson.net/tjrobinson.net/content/blog/2012-10-05-powershell-contains-vs-match-and-like/index.md","fields":{"slug":"/2012-10-05-powershell-contains-vs-match-and-like/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Powershell: -contains vs. -match and -like"}},"next":{"fileAbsolutePath":"/home/runner/work/tjrobinson.net/tjrobinson.net/content/blog/2013-02-24-beware-of-non-breaking-spaces-in-your-hosts-file/index.md","fields":{"slug":"/2013-02-24-beware-of-non-breaking-spaces-in-your-hosts-file/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Beware of non-breaking spaces in your HOSTS file"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}